text: High Temple Guard (Order of the Albatross)
One of the hundreds of strange fish that populates the dark waters of the World, it has a light on top of its head for luring in prey.
These men are often too ill or sickly to be admitted on board of any vessel, yet their fanatism towards Manann might proof useful in some other capacity.
Considered the alma mater of a strange fish that populates the dark waters of the World, the Augus Fish are the Patrons of Lileath.
The legendary Red Chaos Whale haunts the seven seas tirelessly, serving Stromfel for eternity.
